			"updated_at": "2026-03-17T12:54:41Z",
			"body": "> @mrjo118 All a bit strange given that desktop pre-release 3.6.6 is just out including a strikingly similar fix (#10562) for Windows 🤔\r\n\r\nThat fix is a little different. That fixes properties being lost when switching from RTE to the Markdown editor. The markdown editor should be lossless, but when you make changes in the RTE, it will make structural changes to the raw markdown and probably can lose some html as well",
